high_descs: Turn around and take a right turn to enter the dining room to reach the shelf on the left.
Pick up the potato from the top shelf.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to face the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the Potato in the Microwave.

high_descs: Walk through the living room, into the kitchen and up to the shelf.
Pick up the potato from the shelf above the microwave.
Turn around, then walk over to the fridge.
Place the potato in the refrigerator, close the door, then retrieve it again.
Turn around, walk over to the microwave.
Place the potato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cool off a potato in the refrigerator that will be placed in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and go into the room straight ahead on the left and go to the shelf with the microwave on.
Pick up the potato on the bookshelf.
Turn around and go to the fridge behind you.
Put the potato in the refrigerator, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cool a potato in the refrigerator then put it in the microwave.
